&lt;p&gt;The Emergency Department at Morriston Hospital has an exciting opportunity for Registered Paediatric Nurses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit motivated individuals who are looking for experience in Emergency Care who have the ability to work as part of a team and show leadership and dedication in the Paediatric Emergency Care environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The sucessful candidate will work closely with the Lead Peadiatric ED Consultant to develop and improve the Childrens Emergency provision in ED. They will provide direct patient care in line with Paediatic guidelines whilst supporting unsceduled care targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Individuals who are sucessful will have the opportunity to develop a training and rotational programme to support staff and encouage recruitment and retention in order to mantain a sustainable 24 hour Paediatric service in ED.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
